# Conclusion

The Notes API application was successfully containerized using Docker and Docker Compose. The implementation includes a multi-stage Docker build, PostgreSQL containerization, health checks, persistent volumes, and documentation. The final solution satisfies all task requirements and can be reproduced using the provided configuration and commands.
